@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC" as ATCC
participant ":System" as System

activate ATCC
ATCC -> System : getRouteHistory(routeId)
activate System

note right of System: The system retrieves all historical versions\nof the route, ordered by date descending.

System --> ATCC : returns list of route versions (history)
deactivate System
deactivate ATCC
@enduml
